00:00:08.060 --> 00:00:09.100
Business travel?

00:00:09.100 --> 00:00:12.960
Commuting to the office so you don't miss filing that TPS report?

00:00:12.960 --> 00:00:14.440
Yeah, those are bad.

00:00:14.440 --> 00:00:21.360
