And we had like all these ideas to look to this because the space we're in, they had like an open LDAP installation for the members.

00:12:42.540 --> 00:12:47.640
So we, at one point, we kind of hooked this up so that when you walked in or tapped to RFID card,

00:12:47.640 --> 00:12:51.780
because you could make that speak to the speakers, you could have like your theme song walk in, right?

00:12:51.780 --> 00:12:53.880
Or you could have like loads of silly ideas like that.

00:12:53.880 --> 00:12:58.680
Because if you could, yeah, I mean, it's, if you can think of an entire building as like a gigantic Linux box,

00:12:58.680 --> 00:13:00.540
then there's kind of fun things you can do.

00:13:00.540 --> 00:13:01.620
Yeah, that's really clever.

00:13:01.620 --> 00:13:02.260
I like it.

